Detailed Description

Header file that exposes the public interface of the BGP Stream Prefix Sets.

There is one set for each bgpstream_pfx type (Storage, IPv4 and IPv6).

Author
Chiara Orsini

Definition in file bgpstream_utils_pfx_set.h.
